{
  "texts": [
    "IntroductionIn the diagnosis of many diseases in the field of medicine, a correct diagnosis can be made using pathological images.",
    "The cell nuclei in pathological images are also examined in the diagnosis of many diseases such as Alzheimer's and diabetes.",
    "In the literature, many different diseases can be diagnosed by only looking at the cell nucleus [1].",
    "This is why cell segmentation is a very important issue in the field of medicine.",
    "The study of cell nuclei is also important in the pharmaceutical industry."
  ]
}